<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Default" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Default,</orth> fault: <cit><quote>we are penitent for your d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this was your d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Talbot perisheth by your d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.4.28" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 28</bibl></cit>. <emph>in the d.</emph> == at a need: <cit><quote>that I may say in the d. he is a man I know,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.242" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 242</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>